\cl CHAPTER 4
\p
\v 1 ¶ Furthermore, then, we beseech you, brethren, and exhort \add you\add* by the Lord Jesus, that as ye have received from us how ye ought to walk and to please God, as also ye are walking, \add so\add* ye would abound more and more.
